      "body": "https://github.com/wbl/roughtime-draft/blob/695381624a2478973d7f090dc60725746a4433d8/draft-ietf-ntp-roughtime.md?plain=1#L537\r\n\r\n\"ZZZZ\" is 0x5a5a5a5a in hex, not 0x7a7a7a7a. This is \"zzzz\".\r\n\r\nThe intention is probably \"ZZZZ\", so the table should be updated to 0x5a5a5a5a.",
