    {
      "number": 2,
      "id": "PR_kwDOLYaY4c5onxTF",
      "title": "Add support for key multiplexing",
      "url": "https://github.com/wbl/roughtime-draft/pull/2",
      "state": "MERGED",
      "author": "cjpatton",
      "authorAssociation": "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "assignees": [],
      "labels": [],
      "body": "Resolves https://github.com/aanchal4/draft-roughtime/issues/46.\r\n\r\nAdd multi-tenancy as an operational consideration. The idea is that if multiple servers share the same IP or port space, then the client needs a way to indicate which server it expects to respond to a request.\r\n\r\nTo resolve this, define a new request tag, SRV, that indicates the DNS name associated with long-term public key the client expects to verify the response with.",
      "createdAt": "2024-03-04T18:02:33Z",
      "updatedAt": "2024-05-13T16:37:30Z",
      "baseRepository": "wbl/roughtime-draft",
