              "originalPosition": 37,
              "body": "Fixed the typo.\r\n\r\nFrom CF's perspective, the goal is be able to support multiple long-term keys on the same IP and port. It's fine if the mapping from long-term public keys to DNS names is 1:1.\r\n\r\nAlso, matches your suggestion here: https://mailarchive.ietf.org/arch/msg/ntp/K1InWKz-VKdL20KgSqj6AV0p4cs/",
              "createdAt": "2024-03-04T20:27:18Z",
              "updatedAt": "2024-03-04T20:27:18Z"
            }
