              "originalPosition": 37,
              "body": "I think 1:1 mapping is perfectly fine, and I don't mind using the DNS name this way. If you don't think this would work, I think the best alternative is to replace `dns_name` input to the hash with the long-lived public key.\r\n\r\nWhat would you like to do? Do you have a suggestion for an alternative?",
